WEBVTT

1
00:15:38.260 --> 00:15:40.360 
把她弄成黑白的  其他的保持彩色
Make her black and white, everything else in color.

2
00:15:42.690 --> 00:15:43.810 
艾丽西娅写给威尔
Alicia to Will:

3
00:15:44.010 --> 00:15:45.880 
这周你出差了
"You were away at depos this week

4
00:15:45.990 --> 00:15:48.260 
我的脑海中全是你的手抚摸着我
All I could think about is your hands on me."

5
00:15:48.260 --> 00:15:49.940 
有时候觉得这很危险
Sometimes this feels too dangerous.

6
00:15:49.940 --> 00:15:50.980 
编辑室
Editing.

7
00:15:53.160 --> 00:15:54.380 
你最好出去看看
You'd better get out there.

8
00:15:54.400 --> 00:15:56.940 
她在计划使用那些非法取得的邮件
She is planning to use illegally obtained e-mails.

9
00:15:56.940 --> 00:15:58.220 
不只是使用而已  还想传播出去
Not just use-- broadcast.

10
00:15:58.220 --> 00:15:59.180 
这种做法已经违反了法律
Which is so far beyond the pale,

11
00:15:59.180 --> 00:16:00.630 
我不敢相信我们居然在谈论这种事情
I can't believe we're having this conversation.

12
00:16:00.630 --> 00:16:01.980 
我没有黑她的邮件
I-I didn't hack her e-mails--

13
00:16:01.980 --> 00:16:03.040 
我只是收到了这些邮件的副本
I just received copies of them.

14
00:16:03.040 --> 00:16:04.900 
-这有什么区别  -区别可大了
- A distinction without a difference. - Well, no.

15
00:16:04.900 --> 00:16:06.360 
最高法院对此做出过裁定
The Supreme Court has spoken to this.

